data.description: Be prepared to call 4858 Hackberry Circle home after your showing appointment.  This well maintained and loved home nestled in a cul-de-sac has lots of room for the family & friends to entertain.  On the main floor you will find an eat in kitchen w island that flows to an oversized living room. A formal dining room that could also be used as an office! Upstairs you will find large bedrooms with walk in closets + additional storage closets.  The master bedroom is oversized to hold your king size furniture. The master bath has his/her sinks, jacuzzi tub and separate shower.  Downstairs you will find a bonus room with storage closets that could be used for a 4th bedroom/teen hangout/man cave. Updated garage doors, kitchen appliances, HVAC{upstairs}, kitchen flooring, master bedroom carpet. Security cameras/doorbell. All of this & much more. Additional photos scheduled - Active 5/6 AGENTS PLEASE REFER TO NOTES FOR SPECIFIC DETAILS OF PROPERTY.
